Corée du Nord eyebaki na kokima epekiselo ya etumbu ya molongo na koleka na nzela ya ba banque ya RDC, elobi na rapport na yango The Sentry ONG oyo elandelaka makambo ya blanchiment d’argent (makoambo ma kolekisa misolo na nzela molili). 
 The Sentry ebimisi mbeba esalamaki mbala mingi mpo na bozangi ekenge na basungi ya président ya kala Joseph Kabila.
Mpo ne The Sentry, yango esalamaki mpe "na kaniaka eye basungi ba Joseph Kabila bamikotisa na kati", mpe "babukaki mikano mya Nations unies, union européenne mpe ya Etats-Unis", ekomi The Sentry.
"Corée du Nord elekaki na nzela ya compagnie na yango Congo Aconde mpo na kokota na système financier international," elobi The Sentry.
Congo Aconde efungolaki compte na Afriland First Bank mpo na yango.
"Ntango ba banques ekoki te kotosa maye masengeli kosalama na alima -mpe soki mbulamatari ekangi miso- crime organisé mpe financement ya terrorisme ekokende nde liboso," elobi moko na bakeli na The Sentry, George Clooney. 
"Bokanisa te ata ngonga moko ete kaniaka mpe kolekisa misolo na nzela molili na esika lokola RDC ekozala na mbano te na mokili te." ekebisi M. Clooney.